** APC UPS RUNTIME CRITICAL ALERT **

Device:    ${NodeName}
IP:        ${IP_Address}
Location:  ${Location}
Time:      ${DateTime}

CRITICAL: This UPS has less than 6 minutes of battery runtime remaining.

This device is likely running on battery power due to a power outage
or power quality issue at this location.

Immediate actions required:
  1. Verify power status at location: ${Location}
  2. Begin graceful shutdown of connected equipment if power
     cannot be restored immediately
  3. Contact facilities if power outage is confirmed

Runtime threshold: 36000 timeticks = 6 minutes
Adjust if more shutdown time is needed:
  60000  = 10 minutes
  180000 = 30 minutes

APC Device Web UI: http://${IP_Address}

-- SolarWinds Automated Alert

** APC UPS RUNTIME ALERT CLEARED **

Device:    ${NodeName}
IP:        ${IP_Address}
Location:  ${Location}
Time:      ${DateTime}

UPS battery runtime has returned above the 6 minute threshold.
The device appears to be charging or restored to utility power.

Please verify the device and connected equipment are operating normally.

APC Device Web UI: http://${IP_Address}

-- SolarWinds Automated Alert
